++ File State

File state refers to the conditions, properties and other metadata of a file. States include:
    * opened
    * downloading
    * scanning
    * encrypting
    * editing
    * uploading
    * decompressing
    * compressing
    * indexing
    * writing
    * reading
    * erasing

